t the standards of the debate about interdisciplinarity for years to come.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aHistory of education. 0aSpecial aspects of education. 0aTheory and practice of education. 7aEDUCATION / Higher.2bisacsh1 aFoshay, Raphael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2012z978311127413308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2012z978311127716540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781926836478423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781926836478/original  a978-3-11-127413-3  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2012b2012  a978-3-11-127716-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2012b2012  aGBV-deGruyter-alles